pr_title: Improve LinksList, Footer, Description and LetterAvatar components
pr_body:
Make improvements in LinksList, Footer, Description, and LetterAvatar Components

## Description
Add null-checks, prop-types to all these components, make them more reusable via props, make the footer dynamic, add icon in the links list, improve the styles of description and make the letter avatar to be always capitalized

## Motivation and Context
Improve the current components functionally and make them customizable via props, also create documentation for the same

## Types of changes

- [x] Bug fix (non-breaking change which fixes an issue)
- [x] New feature (non-breaking change which adds functionality)
- [ ] Breaking change (fix or feature that would cause existing functionality to change)

## Screenshots
![main](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/62200066/121037394-0c172a80-c7cd-11eb-9ee5-570846e658e9.png)
Home page is no more blank

![footer](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/62200066/121037632-39fc6f00-c7cd-11eb-9245-7429f32c78ac.png)
Footer dynamically shows the current year

![mailing](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/62200066/121037895-76c86600-c7cd-11eb-99ae-dba559599d65.png)
Mailing feed is made reusable to take half space based on props

![avatar](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/62200066/121038107-a37c7d80-c7cd-11eb-8a0b-f78e656d0a67.png)
The avatar will always be capitalized now

pr_title: Improve ImageGrid, ImageAvatar, Previous Projects and GitterRoom, Guidelines, Mailing-list and create a search bar component
pr_body:
## Description
This PR makes the existing ImageGrid component more reusable via props and also passing texts, created a new reusable ImageAvatar component, add previous projects featured on the IdeaList component and update the GitterRoomList to show all the rooms for an organization, improves the button component to set the width of button using props, create a reusable search bar and add the search functionality to the team list component, improves the guidelines component to also have an optional image field.

## Motivation and Context
Improving the existing components functionally and adding search functionality
